      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this honest and reliable ride! This car is a fantastic value for anyone looking for a functional vehicle with plenty of character. While it shows some visible signs of use and could use a little cosmetic attention, it remains a sturdy choice for your daily needs. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a dependable car at an accessible price point!",
