    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owners. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only minor wear on the upholstery and touchpoints. Mechanically, the car performs reliably with no known issues, making it a solid choice for anyone seeking a dependable and well-kept vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
